%
故P(X = 3) = \frac{60}{125} = \frac{12}{25}，
%
所以E(X) = 1 \times P(X = 1) + 2 \times P(X = 2) + 3 \times P(X = 3)
%
= 1 \times \frac{5}{125} + 2 \times \frac{12}{25} + 3 \times \frac{12}{25} = \frac{61}{25}.\frac{61}{25}.
%
法二：依题意，假设随机变量X_{i}，其中i = 1,2,3,4,5：
%
