%
因此球i至少被取出一次的概率为：\)P\left( X_{i} = 1 \right) = 1 - \frac{64}{125} = \frac{61}{125}\(，
%
故\)E\left\lbrack X_{i} \right\rbrack = \frac{61}{125}\(，
%
所以\)E\lbrack X\rbrack = 5E\left\lbrack X_{i} \right\rbrack = 5 \times \frac{61}{125} = \frac{61}{25}\(.\)\frac{61}{25}\(.\)}
